sentences: Tyler Mathew Carl Williams (born February 25, 1988), professionally known as T-Minus, is a Canadian record producer.

He has produced hit records and worked with many popular artists including Lil Wayne,  Eminem, Drake, Nicki Minaj, The Weeknd, Kendrick Lamar, Camila Cabello, Travis Scott, Justin Bieber, Belly, ASAP Rocky, Big Sean, DJ Khaled, 2 Chainz, Lana Del Rey, Sia, J. Cole, and more.

After sitting at the drum kit for a few years, he decided to try making his own rhythms, so he downloaded a digital audio workstation program called Fruity Loops when he was 15 years old and was soon creating entire songs.
